programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The “passion choir pilot program” trains students from three underperforming schools’ choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the “passion choir” and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Shark Busters
programme.desc: During the financial crisis, a vast majority of Hong Kong people experience difficulties in repaying debts. During this time, loan sharks use ruthless ways to force debtors to repay their loans and it is up to Officer Lee and his underground team to hunt down the head of this illegal organization.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the “midnight gymnasium” programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu works in London but is set to be deported back to China due to problems of his visa. His best friend, Jin, is a UK citizen and suggests disguising as a couple with Gu to secure his stay. Everything goes well until Gu falls for his neighbour and Jin’s parents pay a surprise visit. The two men begin to doubt if they should tell the truth.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his father’s death…

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness…

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kit’s master, Debo.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap…

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the façade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Doubles Cause Troubles
programme.desc: Two squabbling cousins find themselves in more trouble than they can imagine after their tenant ends up dead. The gangsters and the police are both after them, and they have no idea what they have done wrong!

programme.title: Knockout
programme.desc: A former boxing champion and convict who has just been released from prison discovers that his wife has died and he is now a single parent. The situation is made worse with his daughter’s diagnosis of leukaemia. In order to encourage his daughter and fulfil his promise of never giving up, he re-enters the boxing ring.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Mei’s dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child. It is only through the child’s unintentional help that the couple finally manages to salvage their relationship.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his father’s remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn…

programme.title: Mother VS Mother
programme.desc: Guan De Xing fell in love with Li Xiao Yun when he was young, but was opposed by his mother and had to marry Zhou Shen Yu. Since then, Li holds a grudge against Zhou. Unfortunately, the son of Guan and Zhou falls in love with Li’s daughter, and as the two mothers meet, they start brawling again!

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Hong Kong Hong Kong
programme.desc: After moving to Hong Kong, illegal immigrant Mang has no choice but to live in cramped quarters with male migrants who abuse her. In order to attain Hong Kong residency and a better life, she agrees to marry a lonely old carpenter. After her marriage, Mang crosses paths again with her ex-lover, and the two develop a passionate affair...

programme.title: Legally Declared Dead
programme.desc: Insurance agent Sean visits Tak and Ling's home to follow up on a case and is shocked to see their son's corpse hanging above him. He suspects them of murdering their son to claim the insurance money and decides to launch his own investigation. As he becomes obsessed over their guilt, his kind nature is used against him by the real perpetrator.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The “passion choir pilot program” trains students from three underperforming schools’ choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the “passion choir” and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: Dummy Mommy, without a Baby
programme.desc: Fong Lai Kuen works at an advertising agency but is about to be sacked by her boss after offending him. She pretends to be pregnant so that the company cannot fire her, according to the labour law. Since then, Fong receives much care and love from her colleagues and begins to feel guilty about her lie as things develop out of her expectations.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Shark Busters
programme.desc: During the financial crisis, a vast majority of Hong Kong people experience difficulties in repaying debts. During this time, loan sharks use ruthless ways to force debtors to repay their loans and it is up to Officer Lee and his underground team to hunt down the head of this illegal organization.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say “yes”?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the “midnight gymnasium” programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Special Couple
programme.desc: Gu works in London but is set to be deported back to China due to problems of his visa. His best friend, Jin, is a UK citizen and suggests disguising as a couple with Gu to secure his stay. Everything goes well until Gu falls for his neighbour and Jin’s parents pay a surprise visit. The two men begin to doubt if they should tell the truth.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Hong Kong
programme.desc: This is a story of ICAC investigators fighting against rampant corruption in early 1970s’ Hong Kong. A police sergeant teams up with a triad boss to make billions of dollars in bribes. As a lawyer joins his friend in ICAC to investigate their collusion and fight against corruption, the battle between the righteous and the wicked has just begun.

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Leio
programme.desc: An ex-singer Kao returns to his hometown for a funeral and takes part in a water drilling contest to save his drought-stricken hometown, as well as to win a million dollar cash prize. However, what Kao and other contestants do not realize is that there is a fierce and deadly beast lurking underground who wants to eat them all!

programme.title: Curi-Curi Kesempatan
programme.desc: Cerita Andy dan Martin yang dikerjai oleh Robin dan membuat mereka berdua harus menyamar menjadi perempuan dengan maksud melarikan diri. Mereka menyelinap ke dalam rombongan artis yang akan tour. Berharap akan mendapatkan salah satu gadis-gadis itu membuat kelucuan itu terjadi.

programme.title: Pantai Selatan

Anak tersebut bernama Larasati yang wujudnya cantik hingga membuat banyak orang menggodanya, namun setiap orang yang menggodanya akan mati dikarenakan dendam ibunya yang belum terlaksana.

programme.title: Kanan Kiri Ok 2

Banyolan berkisar pada kesalahpahaman yang sengaja diciptakan agar menimbulkan gelak tawa, terlebih lagi dengan hadirnya Doyok dan Kadir.

programme.title: Sunan Kalijaga & Syech Siti Jenar

programme.title: Kuntilanak 2 (2019)
programme.desc: Di film pertama, Dinda berhasil lolos dari teror kuntilanak. Ia kemudian berniat menemui Karmila yang diyakini sebagai ibu kandungnya. Sialnya, Dinda yang berangkat bersama adik dan temannya malah terjebak dalam rumah di tengah hutan. Kejanggalan mulai terjadi di rumah tersebut. Dinda harus kembali berhadapan dengan kuntilanak.

programme.title: Cinta Kembar
programme.desc: Rhoma Irama sukses besar sebagai musikus dangdut. Kedua adiknya, Deddy dan Herry penuh semangat berlatih karena ingin mengikuti jejak sang kakak. Sebagai remaja, keduanya tak lepas dengan masalah asmara. Kakak-beradik ini mempunyai pacar gadis kembar, Ela dan Eli. Pada saat orang tua Ela dan Eli ingin menjodohkan salah satu anak kembarnya dengan pria lain, mereka menolak, karena cinta kedua pasangan itu sudah begitu mendalam. Cobaan Deddy bukan saja datang dari orang tua Eli, tetapi datang pula dari pemuda lain terhadap Eli.

programme.title: Soekarno
programme.desc: Soekarno berperan penting dalam kemerdekaan Indonesia, dengan dibantu sahabat-sahabatnya. Dalam kisah ini juga ada sosok perempuan yang selalu mendukung karir dari soekarno yaitu Inggit dan Fatmawati, konflik juga sempat terjadi dalam kisah asmara Soekarno. Hingga pada akhirnya Indonesia bisa merdeka pada tanggal 17 Agustus 1945 dengan ditandakan pembacaan proklamasi oleh Soekarno.

programme.title: Video Maut
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Doni yang memiliki keinginan untuk membuat video mesum dengan kekasihnya Maya di sebuah villa. Maya merupakan gadis lugu yang dikerjai oleh Doni. Di villa itu maya tidak sendiri namun mengajak temanya dan membuat rencana Doni berantakan, akhirnya ia membuat rencana agar teman-teman maya pergi dan melancarkan aksinya. Saat Doni merayu Maya dan memulai membuat video munculah sosok menyeramkan. Doni dan maya akhirnya gila. Video itu tersebar di dunia maya, dan barang siapa yang menontonya akan mati dibunuh oleh sosok menyeramkan di video itu.

programme.title: Terang Kasih
programme.desc: Siraman rohani Kristen yang berkaitan dengan kehidupan untuk mendekatkan diri kepada Tuhan Yesus Kristus. Program ini akan dibagi menjadi beberapa bagian, antara lain kesaksian, renungan, serta konseling yang akan dipandu oleh dua orang host

programme.title: STB (Sangat Tidak Biasa)
programme.desc: Program ini menghadirkan kompilasi informasi berbagai macam issue dan topik yang akan dibahas dari berbagai sisi dan dipaparkan oleh penyulih suara.

programme.title: Seru! (Semua Harus Tau)
programme.desc: Program informasi dokumenter yang menyajikan berbagai informasi disertai dengan pemaparannya. Program ini membahas berbagai hal yang seru dan unik yang dilihat dari berbagai sisi serta dipaparkan oleh VO (Voice Over). Selain menghibur, program ini juga kaya akan pengetahuan sehingga akan menambah banyak wawasan bagi pemirsa.

programme.title: Boba (Bombastis Banget)
programme.desc: BOBA (BOMBASTIS BANGET) merupakan program yang berisi informasi ringan yang menyajikan video-video bombastis yang viral, lucu, dan unik dari sosial media. Bisa berupa video kejadian yang tidak biasa ataupun video yang sedang viral. Video-video tersebut akan dikomentari dengan menggunakan VO (voice over) dan dikemas dengan editing yang kekinian.

programme.title: Superbook
programme.desc: Animasi religi kristen yang menceritakan petualangan seru Chris dan Joy, bersama robot mereka Gizmo. Melalui sebuah alat bernama Superbook, mereka bertiga mampu menjelajah lorong waktu, bertemu dengan tokoh-tokoh Alkitab, dan menjadi saksi mata sejarah. Melalui petualangan mereka inilah, Superbook membawa pesan Alkitab kepada generasi anak-anak di era digital.

programme.title: Metal Cardbot
programme.desc: Dahulu kala, terdapat sebuah planet bernama Machina dimana Metal Cardbots tinggal. Suatu ketika, planet ini tiba-tiba meledak dan memaksa semua penghuninya untuk hidup di Bumi. Agar tidak menarik perhatian makhluk Bumi, Cardbots menyamar sebagai kendaraan sehari-hari. Hingga suatu hari, seorang anak sekolah dasar yang bernama Jun secara tidak sengaja menemukan Metal Breath, dengan Metal Breath tersebut dia bisa menangkap dan menyalakan Cardbots dengan kemampuan yang berbeda.

programme.title: Pokemon Horizons
programme.desc: Petualangan seru dengan karakter karakter baru yang berlatar di dunia Pokémon yang sudah dikenal dan menyenangkan Baik Liko maupun Roy memiliki benda benda misterius yang masing masing sebuah liontin dan Poké Ball yang tampak unik tetapi untuk mengungkap makna benda benda tersebut Liko harus mengambil langkah pertama yang berani Sepanjang perjalanan Liko dan Roy bertemu Friede Kapten Pikachu, dan Amethio Dengan dunia Pokémon yang luas sebagai panggung mereka Liko dan Roy memulai petualangan baru mereka Pertemuan dan takdir apa yang akan terjadi Di sinilah kisah petualangan baru dan penemuan apa yang benar benar penting dimulai

programme.title: Ultraman Arc
programme.desc: Ultraman Arc bercerita tentang Yuma Hize yang bergabung ke Pusat Investigasi dan Pencegahan Kaiju Ilmiah (SKIP). Dalam sebuah tugas, secara tidak sengaja Yuma Hize bergabung dengan raksasa cahaya dari galaksi yang jauh dan bertransformasi menjadi Ultraman Arc.

programme.title: Cai Yoo (Cerita Anak Indonesia Yoo Yoo Yoo)
programme.desc: Program hiburan yang edukatif yang disajikan bagi penonton anak-anak, dipandu oleh seorang host yang akan mendatangi sekolah-sekolah untuk mengajak siswa bermain sambil belajar bersama. Program ini akan menampilkan praktik sains dari kakak Ilmuwan, pertunjukan dongeng, hingga pertunjukan bakat siswa seperti menyanyi, menari, berolahraga, dll. Pada setiap bagian program terdapat pembelajaran bagi siswa yang dikemas lebih menyenangkan.

programme.title: Cloud Bread
programme.desc: Animasi yang menceritakan sebuah keluarga kucing. Kakak beradik yang bernama Hongbi dan Hongsi. Hongbi menjadi kakak yang baik bagi Hongsi.

programme.title: Bola Kampung
programme.desc: Cerita ini berlatar di Kampung Gong Lechar di daerah Pohon Bambu. Berkisah tentang sekelompok remaja yang memiliki hasrat besar terhadap sepak bola untuk bersenang-senang. Kemudian kepala sekolah, Pak Doud, dan pelatih yang baru diangkat, Pak Abdul Rahman, memutuskan untuk membentuk tim sepak bola yang akan mewakili mereka dalam kompetisi antar sekolah. Iwan memimpin tim dalam perjuangannya menjadi tim terbaik di tingkat kabupaten. Sayangnya, mimpi Iwan ditentang oleh ayahnya, Azman, karena ayahnya tidak ingin Iwan menjadi sepertinya yang memiliki nasib tragis sehingga karir sepak bolanya tercoreng. Namun dengan dukungan teman-temannya, Azizul dan Sabok, Iwan berhasil mengatasi masalah dan muncul sebagai tulang punggung tim. Dengan kebersamaan, tim berusaha untuk mengatasi tantangan yang menghadang demi mencapai impiannya.

programme.title: Makan Mulu
programme.desc: Makan Mulu merupakan program yang menyajikan berbagai referensi kuliner serta jajanan yang kekinian, dan menjelajah tempat-tempat kuliner yang unik dan viral. Perjalanan ini tambah seru karena beragam kuliner dan lokasinya akan di review oleh seorang Food Vloger/Chef/Food Expert yang seru dan ekspresif.

programme.title: Skena
programme.desc: SKENA (Sekolah Kece Penuh Warna) merupakan program variety show yang menampilkan berbagai bakat unggulan dari siswa-siswi di sekolah tersebut. Selain ini, program ini juga menampilkan bintang tamu rahasia di setiap sekolahnya. Program ini akan dipandu oleh seorang host yang lucu, seru dan tentunya bisa bonding dengan anak SMP dan SMA.

programme.title: Pokemon Master Journey
programme.desc: Kisah ini tentang seorang bocah lelaki berusia 10 tahun “Ash” yang bertekad untuk menjadi Pokémon Master terhebat di dunia dan “Goh” seorang bocah lelaki yang bermimpi menangkap semua Pokémon di dunia dan Pikachu kedua anak laki-laki itu akan memulai perjalanan ke dunia Pokémon yang sangat besar, tempat misteri dan petualangan menanti mereka.

programme.title: Metal Cardbot
programme.desc: Dahulu kala, terdapat sebuah planet bernama Machina dimana Metal Cardbots tinggal. Suatu ketika, planet ini tiba-tiba meledak dan memaksa semua penghuninya untuk hidup di Bumi. programme.title: Ejen Ali
programme.desc: Serial animasi dengan tokoh utama bernama Ali yang tidak sengaja menjadi agen Meta Advance Tactical Agency (MATA). Ali membuktikan diri bahwa Ia mampu menjadi agen MATA dan mengalahkan musuh bersama Alicia dan Paman bakar

programme.title: Boboiboy Galaxy The Movie
programme.desc: BoBoiBoy Galaxy merupakan sebuah kisah tentang robot-robot Power Sphera yang dibuat untuk memberikan kekuasaan besar kepada pemiliknya. Namun, proyek Power Sphera akhirnya dianggap sebagai proyek yang berbahaya dan dibatalkan, sedangkan Power Sphera yang lain melarikan diri dan bersembunyi di berbagai pelosok galaksi.

programme.title: Mechamato
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang menceritakan seorang anak laki-laki bernama Amato dalam menemukan sebuah pesawat ruang angkasa penjara berisi robot-robot jahat yang telah jatuh ke bumi. Salah satu robot tersebut adalah MechaBot yang memiliki kemampuan untuk mengubah objek sehari-hari menjadi perangkat berteknologi tinggi. Amato berhasil menginovasi MechaBot menjadi master MechaBot. Sejak itu, MechaBot dan Amato mulai bekerja sama untuk menemukan dan menangkap robot jahat.

programme.title: Check In (Check Informasi)
programme.desc: Program yang menyajikan fakta-fakta unik tentang fenomena serta isu terkini yang terjadi di dunia melalui video-video yang bersumber dari media sosial dan dipaparkan oleh Voice Over (VO) yang unik. Check In juga akan mengajak interaksi dengan masyarakat melalui VoxPop tentang tema yang dibahas.

programme.title: Takdir Cinta Kera Sakti
programme.desc: 500 tahun yang lalu, Zi Xia turun ke bumi untuk menemukan Zhi Zun Bao, kekasihnya yang berhasil mengeluarkan pedang Zi Qing. Seiring berjalannya waktu, pedang Zi Qing rusak. Untuk memperbaikinya, Zi Xia menggunakan Kotak Pandora untuk menjelajah waktu, yang membuatnya terjebak di masa 500 tahun mendatang. Di sana ia bertemu Zhi Zun Bao, namun ia samasekali tidak ingat akan masa lalunya. Selain tidak ingat akan masa lalunya, ia sekarang adalah pemimpin kelompok pemberontak Bernama Ax Gang. Cerita berlanjut dengan lebih banyak penjelajahan waktu dan kejadian tak terduga!
